       the output should get censored. In that case the output must be censored
       in that way you said in less than 24 hours.
This License acknowledges your rights of fair use or other equivalent, as
provided by copyright law.

3. Modified versions

Source code must be made available when the modified
program is distributed in any way.
A copy of the above copyright notice must be included with the modified program.
The modified program's license must meet these requerements:
